message: Revised throughout. I am the subject of what I believe to be a highly biased page that I am now changing.
I am David Gushee and I am not happy with the recent edits to my page. I am beginning a revision. Began with the opening sentence and will return later.
The current entry contains errors, is biased against Gushee, overemphasizes the LGBT controversy, and contains incomplete information about his work. These changes substantially improve the page.
